    <title>DfT red tape challenge and logistics growth review commitments</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;We are seeking views on the implementation of three deregulatory commitments in the ‘&lt;a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/consultations/road-transport-red-tape-challenge"&gt;Red tape challenge road transportation regulations and actions consultation response&lt;/a&gt;’, about:&lt;/p&gt;

